ygData.messageBody:
Nice to see you to!
This list has not been very informative in a long time... that last question
I asked, I was thrown at a message board and had to hunt around for a long
time to find out anything, and what I found wasn't very helpful.
*shrug*

I hope things pick up. =) That's why I am still here actually. Hoping. ;-)

--
Uthanatos

Man, I thought this news group was dead. I have been a member now for about
3 weeks and this is the first e-mail I got :-)

I'd like say hello to everyone! My main Char is a level 51 (so close to 52)
Cleric, Micromu and I have a level 41 Warrior, Sistily. Being a Cleric, an
Enchanter is my best friend. I always buff my enchanter with everything I
can and watch his health close and stunning those Mobs that come un-mezzed.

Well, just wanted to say hello!

Micromu
Sistily
Tunare Server
